OL,3,CGame about Islandmagee witch trials to
OL,4,Cbe made freely available to NI schools
OL,6,FA dark chapter of Co Antrim's history
OL,7,Fhas been reimagined in a video game
OL,8,Fdeveloped by Ulster University.
OL,10,FIn 1711, eight women and a man were
OL,11,Fconvicted of bewitching an 18-year-old
OL,12,Fwoman called Mary Dunbar.
OL,14,FThe women's punishment was a year in
OL,15,Fprison and four stints in the pillory,
OL,16,Fwhile it's thought the man was
OL,17,Fprobably executed.
