OL,3,CGame about Islandmagee witch trials to
OL,4,Cbe made freely available to NI schools
OL,6,FThe trial was held in Carrickfergus,
OL,7,Fbut the people involved became known
OL,8,Fas the Islandmagee Witches as most of
OL,9,Fthe them were from that area.
OL,11,FTheir story has been reimagined in
OL,12,F1711 Ireland: A Witch's Fate, a video
OL,13,Fgame that will be made freely
OL,14,Favailable to schools in Northern
OL,15,FIreland.
OL,17,FBased on historical research,
OL,18,Frecreations of Carrickfergus and
OL,19,FIslandmagee during the 1700s have been
OL,20,Fdeveloped for it.
