OL,3,CGame about Islandmagee witch trials to
OL,4,Cbe made freely available to NI schools
OL,6,FDr Andrew Sneddon from Ulster
OL,7,FUniversity, who co-lead the project,
OL,8,Fsaid the people convicted were
OL,9,F"marginal... they were poor, they had
OL,10,Fdisabilities, they were ill-educated".
OL,12,FHe added: "We're not trivializing this
OL,13,Fand it's very sensitively handled.
OL,14,FThat's why it has to be historical as
OL,15,Fwell, because there were 9 people,
OL,16,Freal people, with relatives and lives.
OL,18,F"I see it as partly a commemorative
OL,19,Fpiece as well."
