OL,6,FMeanwhile, Dr Victoria McCollum from
OL,7,FUlster University, who also co-lead
OL,8,Fthe project, said the themes explored
OL,9,Fin the game are relevant to modern
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,F"It was important for us to have a
OL,13,Fplatform to tell a very unique piece
OL,14,Fof Irish cultural history that has so
OL,15,Fmuch resonance today," she said.
