OL,6,F"We live in a very polarized society.
OL,7,FWe do have a problem with violence
OL,8,Fagainst women and girls, and this is a
OL,9,Fgame that's really deeply
OL,10,Fentertaining, but also about power,
OL,11,Fabout gender, about religion, about
OL,12,Fviolence, and about what it actually
OL,13,Fmeans to be othered."
